    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for exceptional throttle response. This example is equipped with the preferred Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including documented rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service. The suspension retains its precision with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the chassis handles with classic M-car poise. While showing minor age-appropriate cosmetic wear, the drivetrain and structural integrity remain excellent for a dedicated driver.",
      "price": 36500.0,
