      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and light surface swirls consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the leather seats remain supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster and no structural tears. All power features, including the dual-zone climate control and infotainment system, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service history that includes a recent synthetic oil change and a cooling system flush. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the suspension provides a firm yet comfortable ride. It is a reliable, attractive, and mechanically sound vehicle ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
