      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This unit has been meticulously maintained to a high standard, ensuring a driving experience that remains both reliable and engaging. With a documented service history and a well-preserved cabin, it represents a superior value proposition for the discerning motorist seeking a balance of sophistication and long-term performance.",
