    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it to get you where you need to go comfortably. It runs like a dream and is just waiting for someone new to take the wheel. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and see it for yourself!",
