      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides precise engagement, while the double VANOS system has been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal cam timing. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to maintain chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. Equipped with the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential and a well-sorted suspension, this car offers the communicative steering and 50/50 weight distribution that defines the chassis. A mechanically robust specimen ready for the discerning enthusiast who prioritizes performance integrity.",
